  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1078">
<l>collap payaṉpaṭuvar cāṉṟōr karumpupōṟ</l>
<l>kollap payaṉpaṭuṅ kīḻ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The great bestow (their alms) as soon as they are informed; (but) the mean, like the sugar-cane, only when they are tortured to death.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
